Happy Saturday, 5 days to MET TGE.

Markets may seem rocky, but I wanted to take this time to acknowledge the beautiful smooth execution this week.

We've managed to champion our core @MeteoraAG narrative better, going from a vague "wall street in your pocket" to tangible reasons why we can achieve it.

Shoutout to our 3 pillars and they're core drivers:
Best LP Army (@0xmiir), Best Tech (@dannxbt), Best Launchpads (@vesper792), and supported by @lochiejarvis201 on main. 

On the engineering side, the frontend team (@senddagee4get, @p) have done an amazing job with met.meteora.ag, its beautiful, its performant and reliable, and we facilitated >100K visits in the first few minutes with no hiccups. 

Beautiful shoutout to Design ( @itsvietquoc, Trung, and more)

Big shoutout to backend @0xkappayield, Chalaka, Hashira & Viet-Anh for their efforts here as well, we were worried that it will go down but it handled everything AMAZINGLY smooth.

Also, a special shout-out to @SuperHighDeFi, the unsung pillar of Meteora who pushed EVERYTHING, from verification of CSV files, to the engineering effort to pull the checker off, to making sure everything was deployed at 8pm SGT exactly.

And of course, the man himself @sudoku_defi (alongside his team @KampungTech, @defi_0x1) for building the Liquidity Distributor, the Merkle Distributor, the DAMM V2 program, and literally everyone that makes Meteora, meteora. 

We had a beautiful and smooth week of execution, I'm super happy to see the community happy with their allocations.

We're not gonna let up, and continue the smooth execution all the way into TGE. Banger after banger awaits. See you on Monday.
